      - M `src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Infrastructure/DI/ComposeModule.cs`
      - A `tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/Services/Compose/DocxTextExtractorTests.cs`
      - M `projects/spaarkeai-compose-r1/current-task.md`
